headline: Mizuho lifts targets on storage and memory stocks on strong AI demand
summary: Investing.com -- Mizuho raised its price targets on key storage and memory stocks, Seagate, Western Digital (NASDAQ:WDC), and SanDisk, in a note Thursday, citing accelerating demand driven by AI infrastructure.
